    "This can be understood from their expression as certain form of summation of TPR and TNR.",
    "Naive random guess is constant around 0.5 and 0, median of the range for balanced accuracy and bookmaker informedness respectively, indicating the amount of prediction accuracy by random chance.",
    "Cohen's Kappa shows an concave curve with respect to prevalence.",
    "That is it is higher when class is more balanced and lower when class is more imbalanced.",
    "From Eq 9, we know that Kappa ¼ Accuracy expAccuracy À 1 1"
